	</p>
	<p class="nation--p">
		<strong>&pound;513.00*</strong> weekly average charge in independent sector residential homes in Wales.
	</p>
	<p class="nation--p">
		If you have assets <strong>above £24,000</strong> you will pay for all your care. If you have assets of <strong>£24,000 or less</strong>, you may be entitled to some financial help from your local authority depending on the level of your income.
	</p>


